room_title: Escape room "Elliot Ness Investigation" by Perplexity Games in Cleveland
room_description: It's 1938 and Cleveland Safety Director Eliot Ness has secretly hired you to investigate a corrupt city commissioner with ties to illegal gambling. You've got an hour to find the evidence needed to take him down and get out safely. If you're caught by the mob you'll be sleeping with the fishes in Lake Erie.
